messages.message: Hey everyone, reminder that when you add links to the documentation you should be adding the routes to docsRoutes.ts (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/webserver/shared/src/js/webpacked/lib/src/constants/docsRoutes.ts) then using the `AihubDocs` constant to access it - this makes it easier to maintain the routes and make sure we're always linking to the right domain. We should never just use plain routes for docs links.
